app_name: Groups Treatment Groups Apple Translate PDF Translator Pro
app_description: Start translating in a matter of seconds! Listen to your documents with our PDF to Voice feature over 500 voices available! With an ease of use navigation you can translate your ebooks contracts manuals or just about any documents. You can choose from over 100 languages. PDF Translator Pro will auto detect the language of your documents. PDF Translator Pro allows you to translate unlimited number of pages in a single document. Your translated files are accessible through the Translation History feature which allows you to access your documents whenever you need them. Once you get your results you can share them on a device or platform of your choice. Not sure about the file you are translating PDF Translator Pro offers Quick Preview on all steps of the translation so you never loose track of your content. Features: Text to Speech QR Code Support Over 100 Languages Scanner feature Merge multiple files Protect your documents Turn any web page into a PDF document No page limits Translation History Easy File Sharing Quick Preview Privacy Policy: https: aldoo.co.uk privacy Terms of Use: https: www.aldoo.co.uk terms of use
